{"tid":199033,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人返工成日整蠱人","createTime":"2017-04-13T01:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T06:27:37.000Z","uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e1fe79053cda83793f0f2f7dbbd3125a380f9f8","tid":199033,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T01:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然唔係害人<br />\n<br />\n有個同事好怕阿飄，之前講過要&ldquo;拷門&rdquo;先敢入房，又話比鬼責<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尋日佢要落下倉，咁我要上上倉<br />\n佢入去先，唔知我跟尾<br />\n下倉要入地牢，好陰暗<br />\n我係上倉扮阿飄叫，嗚&hellip;嗚&hellip;再拍鐵板<br />\n之後我見住佢跑返office <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31985353f852316cc13b92bab30dabddb1475fc5","tid":199033,"uid":12720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T01:37:32.000Z","msg":"做咩姐你"},{"pid":"3eaaea7a2a93a21cbd66ceb4c81ea119af579914","tid":199033,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T01:39:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做咩姐你</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嚇鬼你"},{"pid":"398a30b394b85846de5d262a53e782daf63590a7","tid":199033,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T03:20:34.000Z","msg":"飄你老母"},{"pid":"03754db6ce323ce18658beb6e6e083d31d1f0175","tid":199033,"uid":72327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T03:50:28.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以講返發生咩事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6384089c7158249f92bf81a8b22311eaf550b2c1","tid":199033,"uid":69014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T03:53:57.000Z","msg":"笑撚左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主平日係咪好得閒？小心D, 公司裁員第一個裁你"},{"pid":"7d39ddfde71f79a182aab6f276f7f811b8b132c8","tid":199033,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T04:17:36.